.................Usage......................
                                   
                    GET request to http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/products  will return all products.

                 GET request to http://localhost:5000/api/products/1 will return the product with {"id"} 1

                          POST request to http://localhost:5000/api/products with JSON payload

   PUT request to http://localhost:5000/api/products/1 with JSON payload {"price": 500.99} will update the price of the product with ID
       
                 DELETE request to http://localhost:5000/api/products/1 will delete the product with ID 1.
